      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Interface">Master Machine Angle</text><text styleclass="Popup Box2"> (MMA):</text><text style="font-size:10pt;">&#32;</text>at the bottom, left of the application. </para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text style="font-size:10pt;">The output from the </text><text styleclass="Popup Box2">MMA</text><text style="font-size:10pt;"> increases at a uniform rate from 0 to 360, again and again, when you cycle the model (</text><text styleclass="VariableName-small">ALT+C</text><text style="font-size:10pt;">). It is a virtual machine-axis.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Interface">MMA - Approximate Value</text>: Drag with your cursor along the scale<image src="Red-14-4.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Image Caption">.</text>&#32;</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">The triangle below the <text styleclass="VariableName-small">MMA</text> scale moves as you drag your mouse.</para>
          <para styleclass="Interface">MMA - Exact Value<text styleclass="Popup Box2">:</text><text styleclass="Popup Box"> Read / Write to the data-box</text><image src="Red-14-2.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Popup Box"> to the right of the scale</text><text styleclass="Popup Box2">.</text><text styleclass="Popup Box"> Use the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Spin-Box-Tool" styleclass="Popup Box">Spin-Box tool</link><text styleclass="Popup Box"> to edit with large or small increments.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Interface">Revs</text><text style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;">: the number of complete machines-cycles of the </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small">MMA</text><image src="Red-14-3.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;">. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Interface"><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;">Use </text><text styleclass="Popup Box2">ALT+H</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;"> to move the </text><text styleclass="Popup Box2">MMA=0</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal;"> and </text><text styleclass="Popup Box2">REVS= 0</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text style="font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; color:#008000;">DE: Master-Maschinenachse. Ein Bereich von 0 bis 360.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
